  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to evaluate the therapeutic efficacy and safety of two different
      paracetamol-containing solutions in postoperative dental pain. They will be compared to
      placebo (a dummy treatment which contains no active ingredient).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
